<text top="36" left="303" width="6" height="12" font="1">3</text>
<text top="72" left="90" width="400" height="12" font="1">September 19, 1995, February 1, 1996, September 10, 1996, June 19, 1998 </text>
<text top="84" left="90" width="402" height="12" font="1">and November 27, 1998, in favor of Marta Elena Arrivillaga de Carpio and </text>
<text top="96" left="90" width="127" height="12" font="1">Karen Fischer de Carpio. </text>
<text top="108" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="1"> </text>
<text top="120" left="90" width="16" height="12" font="1">2. </text>
<text top="120" left="126" width="366" height="12" font="1">To request the State to continue to report to the Court every two </text>
<text top="133" left="90" width="396" height="12" font="1">months on the measures that it has taken in this case, and the Inter-</text>
<text top="145" left="90" width="407" height="12" font="1">American Commission on Human Rights to continue to submit its </text>
<text top="157" left="90" width="399" height="12" font="1">observations on that information to the Court, within six weeks of receiving it. </text>
<text top="169" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="1"> </text>
<text top="181" left="90" width="15" height="12" font="1">3. </text>
<text top="181" left="126" width="365" height="12" font="1">To request the State of Guatemala to include detailed information on </text>
<text top="193" left="90" width="400" height="12" font="1">the proceeding by which it adopted the decision to close case No. 1011-97 in </text>
<text top="205" left="90" width="405" height="12" font="1">its next report, together with all the documentation it holds on this </text>
<text top="217" left="90" width="62" height="12" font="1">proceeding. </text>
<text top="230" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="1"> </text>
<text top="242" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="1"> </text>
